headline: Fastenal Names New Chief Financial Officer and Senior Executive Vice President
summary: WINONA, Minn., November 03, 2025--Fastenal Company (Nasdaq: FAST) (the 'Company' or 'Fastenal') has appointed Max Tunnicliff to the position of Chief Financial Officer and Senior Executive Vice President, effective November 10, 2025.
